<p>
<strong>The game is</strong> built up of several biomes, cubic floating islands, where every biome have a puzzle. Each puzzle should craft, or create a path to progress onto the next biome. On the final biome the player can find itœôòùs friends and family, and the demo ends there. 
</p>


<p>
We built the game with a vision of making  
<ol>
<li>Soothing and slow pace with nice scenes and sounds</li>
<li>Problem-solving, puzzle-oriented and limited resource management</li>
<li>Storyline</li>
<li>Catered towards beginner-players</li>
</ol> 

</p>

